to appoint a public defender.

80
00:05:29,590 --> 00:05:31,060
难道留着你做我们的律师
You think we got a better chance

81
00:05:31,090 --> 00:05:32,690
我们会有更大的机会胜诉吗?
if we keep you on as our lawyer?

82
00:05:32,730 --> 00:05:34,730
这要取决于你们
Well, it's up to you.

83
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:37,670
我比谁都要了解这案子的情况
I do know the circumstances of the case better than anyone.

84
00:05:39,870 --> 00:05:44,610
这些邮资信封是用来联系你们家人的
Now, these stamped envelopes are to contact your family members

85
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:47,940
让他们知道你们没被亏待
to assure them you're being well-treated

86
00:05:47,980 --> 00:05:50,510
