and to arrange payment of my retainer.

87
00:05:50,550 --> 00:05:54,120
将五十美元现金送到我的办公室
That's $50 cash receivable at my office.

88
00:05:56,650 --> 00:05:58,650
你们杀了我的儿子们
You killed my sons.

89
00:05:59,820 --> 00:06:01,690
你那些杀人犯儿子
Your murdering sons.

90
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,720
定罪之前任何人都是无罪的
Not guilty till proved innocent,

91
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:06,790
像你这样的人也理应得到公平审判
men like you who deserved a fair trial.

92
00:06:06,830 --> 00:06:09,260
我祈祷你被绞死
I pray you hang.

93
00:06:09,300 --> 00:06:12,600
我会提供造绞刑架的木材
I will supply the lumber for the gallows,

94
00:06:12,630 --> 00:06:14,100
我还会帮你系紧绞绳的结
and I will tie the knot on your rope.

95
00:06:14,140 --> 00:06:17,910
等你脖子断了 我会感到高兴
And when your neck snaps, I will rejoice

96
00:06:17,940 --> 00:06:21,640
因为你将被不灭的地狱之火所焚烧!
as you are sent to boil in eternal damnation's hellfire!

97
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,550
也祝你圣诞快乐 先生
A Merry Christmas to you, too, sir.

98
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:46,700
你没事吧 妈妈? 
You all right, ma?

99
00:06:46,730 --> 00:06:49,770
你听见了吗?
You hear that?

100
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,670
听见什么?
Hear what?

101
00:06:51,300 --> 00:06:53,240
嘘
Shh.

102
00:06:57,610 --> 00:06:59,280
他们会从那边来
They'll come from over there.

103
00:07:00,810 --> 00:07:02,250
谁?
Who will?

104
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:04,650
哈特菲尔德家的人 他们会从那边来
Hatfields, they'll come from over there.

105
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,720
哈特菲尔德家的人?
Hatfields?

106
00:07:06,750 --> 00:07:10,490
妈 哈特菲尔德家的人正躲着恶人弗兰克呢
Ma, Hatfields are hiding out from bad Frank.

107
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:12,460
他们不会过来河这边的
They ain't gonna come across this side of the river.

108
00:07:14,290 --> 00:07:15,660
进去吧 好吗?
Let's go inside, huh?

109
00:07:17,500 --> 00:07:19,160
今晚没有人会来
No one's coming tonight.

110
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:21,530
我不是说今晚
It's not tonight I speak of.

111
00:07:58,640 --> 00:08:02,770
我们就像猎物一样被那些该死的赏金猎人追捕
We're hunted like animals by hired trash.

112
00:08:02,810 --> 00:08:07,410
家人和朋友 或被绑架 或被谋杀
Family and friends kidnapped and murdered.

113
00:08:08,250 --> 00:08:11,150
法律袖手旁观
The law stood by.

114
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:15,120
法律无所作为
The law has done nothing.

115
00:08:15,150 --> 00:08:16,750
尽管如此 如果有什么....
Even so, if there was anything...

116
00:08:18,590 --> 00:08:21,990
我可以付出什么
anything I had that, by giving it,

117
00:08:22,030 --> 00:08:23,560
来结束这场血腥争斗
I could end this bloody struggle,

118
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,160
我会心甘情愿地付出
I would give it gladly.

119
00:08:30,500 --> 00:08:34,400
我愿意献出我的生命来终止这场战争
I'd give my life if it would end this.

120
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:37,410
你不会的
You would not.

121
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:41,040
我不愿意献出的是
What I will not give

122
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:44,580
我族人的哪怕一滴血
is one more drop of this family's blood.

123
00:08:48,690 --> 00:08:51,760
所以今晚
So tonight,

124
00:08:51,790 --> 00:08:55,160
在这新年前夕
this new year's Eve,

125
00:08:55,190 --> 00:08:57,060
让我们了结这一切吧
we end this forever.

126
00:09:00,770 --> 00:09:03,570
我愿意和你一起去 哈特菲尔德先生
Im's with you, Mr. Hatfield.

127
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:05,940
