were taken illegally.

461
00:31:28,700 --> 00:31:30,670
那是文书工作上出现了错误
There was an error of paperwork.

462
00:31:30,700 --> 00:31:32,030
我们的法庭会裁决的
Our courts will adjudicate it.

463
00:31:32,070 --> 00:31:34,640
我的家被烧毁了 可不是文书错误
My house burnin' was no paper error.

464
00:31:37,140 --> 00:31:41,710
法庭无法使我的女儿和我被枪杀的儿子复活
No court can resolve my daughter, my son shot dead,

465
00:31:41,740 --> 00:31:46,110
我的妻子也受了重伤
my wife so grievously injured,

466
00:31:46,150 --> 00:31:50,420
公正的上帝不会允许这些暴行!
atrocities that a just God would not allow!

467
00:31:50,450 --> 00:31:51,620
我们能拍张照片吗 先生?
May we take a photograph, sir?

468
00:31:59,130 --> 00:32:01,230
你的枪
Your weapon.

469
