Our readers will really appreciate this.

471
00:32:06,340 --> 00:32:07,900
把枪稍微拿高一点
Just hold the gun up a little bit higher.

472
00:32:07,940 --> 00:32:09,640
没事的 兰德尔
It's all right, Randall.

473
00:32:09,670 --> 00:32:11,770
展示出我们对于公正的严肃态度
Shows we're serious about justice.

474
00:32:11,810 --> 00:32:13,710
您看上去非常正直 先生
You look righteous, sir.

475
00:32:13,740 --> 00:32:16,280
等会会闪一下
There's going to be a flash.

476
