- Rosie? - Yeah.

481
00:32:44,240 --> 00:32:46,040
需要什么吗?
Anything you need?

482
00:32:46,070 --> 00:32:47,470
她...她很好
She... she's all right.

483
00:32:50,910 --> 00:32:53,110
妈妈
Oh, mama.

484
00:33:03,560 --> 00:33:05,660
我知道在哪能找着吉姆・万斯
I know where you can find Jim Vance.

485
00:33:05,690 --> 00:33:07,630
是吗?
Yeah?

486
00:33:07,660 --> 00:33:09,500
告诉我
Tell me about it.

487
00:33:31,150 --> 00:33:33,250
嗯哼
Uhhuh.

488
00:33:33,290 --> 00:33:35,160
别改变你的步速
Don't alter your pace.

489
00:33:36,190 --> 00:33:38,220
别到处看
Don't look about.

490
00:33:38,260 --> 00:33:41,030
有人躲在我们前面的树后面
There's men concealed in them trees up ahead of us.

491
00:33:41,060 --> 00:33:42,090
是谁? 菲利普斯?
Who is it? Phillips?

492
00:33:42,130 --> 00:33:43,830
大概是他
Most likely.

493
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:48,130
几年前就该杀掉那该死的狐狸
Should have killed that goddamn fox years ago.

494
00:33:48,170 --> 00:33:49,900
听着 盖
Look here, Cap.

495
00:33:49,940 --> 00:33:52,700
交火之后 你得活着
When all this starts, you not being dead,

496
00:33:52,740 --> 00:33:54,170
