趴下 吉姆!
Stay down, Jim!

501
00:34:31,380 --> 00:34:32,940
快跑 盖!
Run, Cap!

502
00:34:32,980 --> 00:34:34,510
逃啊!
Run!

503
00:34:34,550 --> 00:34:37,250
没必要我们两人都在这里吃枪子
No sense in both of us eatin' these bastards' bullets!

504
