吉姆!
Jim!

506
00:34:49,630 --> 00:34:50,630
该死的 孩子!
God damn it, boy!

507
00:34:50,660 --> 00:34:52,160
我说 快逃!
I said, get!

508
00:34:52,200 --> 00:34:54,830
不然我会从地狱回来揍你屁股
Or else I'll come back from hell and tan your hide!

509
00:34:54,870 --> 00:34:55,970
吉姆!
Jim!

510
00:35:06,410 --> 00:35:08,310
把那该死的步枪给我
Give me that damn rifle.

511
00:35:33,770 --> 00:35:34,940
啊 该死的
Ah, shit.

512
00:35:34,970 --> 00:35:36,640
狗娘养的
Son of a bitch.

