I'm terrible sorry,

517
00:35:54,990 --> 00:35:56,160
小嚎尔斯
howls junior.

518
00:35:59,100 --> 00:36:01,230
很抱歉
So sorry.

519
00:36:01,270 --> 00:36:04,630
一切都要结束了
I do believe this is the end of the line.

520
00:36:09,740 --> 00:36:11,440
我紧跟着就来 小家伙
I'll be right behind you, boy.

521
00:36:11,480 --> 00:36:13,440
马上就来
Right behind you.

522
00:36:20,550 --> 00:36:22,790
别开枪
Don't shoot.

523
00:36:23,820 --> 00:36:24,990
