00:39:13,950 --> 00:39:15,020
我懂
I know.

577
00:39:15,050 --> 00:39:15,890
不是 盖或者吉姆...
No, Cap or Jim...

578
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:16,850
我明白
I know.

579
00:39:19,090 --> 00:39:22,230
我知道 因为我很确定
I know, 'cause I made sure.

580
00:39:28,270 --> 00:39:30,500
约翰斯不是叛徒犹大
Johnse's no Judas.

581
00:39:31,970 --> 00:39:36,140
不 他不是 但是有人因他而死 莉瓦西
No, he's not, but people died, Levicy.

582
00:39:36,170 --> 00:39:38,270
但是 你不能说你没有一点责任?
Well, you can't say you didn't have a part in that?

583
00:39:39,140 --> 00:39:42,150
我承认我也有责任
And that I'll have to live with,

584
00:39:42,180 --> 00:39:46,080
但是我俩都知道我们的儿子不是一个谨慎的人
but we both know our boy's not a careful person,

585
00:39:46,620 --> 00:39:49,720
尤其是跟女人在一起的时候
especially around women.

586
00:39:54,430 --> 00:39:57,030
你打算怎么做?
What do you intend to do?

587
00:40:00,500 --> 00:40:02,470
睡吧
Get some sleep.

588
00:40:02,500 --> 00:40:04,470
安德森?
Anderson?

589
00:40:06,540 --> 00:40:08,740
你也睡吧
You should too.

590
00:40:16,410 --> 00:40:19,080
好孩子
Good boy.

591
00:40:39,700 --> 00:40:40,700
嘿 爸爸
Hey, daddy.

592
00:40:41,540 --> 00:40:44,170
你站在那里多久了?
How long you been standing there?

593
00:40:44,210 --> 00:40:46,610
有一会了
A while.

594
00:40:46,640 --> 00:40:49,380
前几天你在哪里?
Where were you the other day?

595
00:40:50,110 --> 00:40:56,090
哦 我去布恩郡寄东西了
Oh, I was up in Boone county making a delivery,

596
00:40:56,520 --> 00:40:58,090
你知道的
you know.

597
00:40:59,420 --> 00:41:01,690
你 唔...
You, uh...

598
00:41:01,730 --> 00:41:04,060
你今天早上要工作吗?
You going to work this morning?

599
00:41:04,900 --> 00:41:08,060
我想我们可以一起去钓鱼
Thought you and me might go fishing.

600
00:41:09,270 --> 00:41:12,230
今天?
Today?

601
00:41:15,110 --> 00:41:18,570
等你干完手上的活 帮我的马装上鞍
When you finish there, saddle my horse.

602
00:41:24,910 --> 00:41:25,780
好的
All right.

603
00:41:40,630 --> 00:41:42,830
你在干什么?
What are you doing?

604
00:41:43,870 --> 00:41:46,130
我和约翰斯需要谈谈
Me and Johnse are gonna have a talk.

605
00:41:46,170 --> 00:41:48,100
我必须知道这是什么意思
I have to know what that means.

606
00:41:49,710 --> 00:41:52,470
你觉得我会伤害他吗?
You think I mean him harm?

607
00:41:52,510 --> 00:41:55,610
不然的话 让我听听是什么
I need to hear otherwise.

608
00:41:58,110 --> 00:42:01,750
我需要听你亲口告诉我
I will hear you say it.

609
00:42:04,350 --> 00:42:07,360
我带他去钓鱼 莉瓦西
I'm taking him fishing, Levicy.

610
00:42:30,550 --> 00:42:32,650
好久不见 哥哥
So long, big brother.

611
00:43:03,740 --> 00:43:05,640
你真的不想钓鱼?
You sure you don't want to fish?

612
00:43:06,080 --> 00:43:08,080
我就来
I'm going to.

613
00:43:08,470 --> 00:43:09,800
还记得上次
You remember the last time

614
00:43:09,840 --> 00:43:12,240
你带我来这个同样的地方钓鱼吗?
you brought me out to this old fishing hole?

615
00:43:14,170 --> 00:43:15,810
我想不起来了
I don't recall that.

616
00:43:15,840 --> 00:43:17,510
我还记得
I do.

617
00:43:17,540 --> 00:43:18,710
我知道 因为我当时坐在
I know, 'cause I was in that

618
00:43:18,740 --> 00:43:21,980
那边的柳树的树枝上
willow tree over there up in that limb.

619
00:43:22,010 --> 00:43:24,680
你记得你跟我说过什么吗?
You recall what you said to me?

620
00:43:26,950 --> 00:43:27,850
我记得
I do.

621
00:43:27,890 --> 00:43:30,030
你说 如果我掉进水里
You said if I fell in,

622
00:43:30,050 --> 00:43:31,420
我会把鱼吓跑的
I was gonna scare the fish.

623
00:43:32,210 --> 00:43:34,710
一旦我掉进去 可别太指望你
And once I was in, chances of you getting me out

624
00:43:34,750 --> 00:43:36,980
会把我救出来 因为你不喜欢
weren't good on account that you were not partial

625
00:43:37,020 --> 00:43:39,720
在冰水里洗澡
to cold water.

626
00:43:39,750 --> 00:43:41,790
你记得你说过这话吗?
You recall having said that?

627
00:43:48,090 --> 00:43:51,960
好吧 我还以为能把你逗笑呢 爸爸
Well, I believe I just coaxed a laugh out of you, pa.

628
00:43:52,000 --> 00:43:54,330
该死 我都不记得上次看你笑是什么时候了
God damn, I don't remember the last time I seen that.

629
00:43:58,700 --> 00:44:00,740
你跟那个麦考伊女孩的结局太糟糕了
It's too bad about you and the McCoy girl.

630
00:44:02,240 --> 00:44:03,270
哪一个?
Which one?

631
00:44:04,910 --> 00:44:06,340
那个跟了别的男人的女孩
The one that ran off with the man

632
00:44:06,380 --> 00:44:08,510
而且还是杀你吉姆叔叔的男人
that killed your uncle Jim.

633
00:44:12,980 --> 00:44:14,880
你记性很好 约翰斯
You recall pretty good, Johnse.

634
00:44:15,990 --> 00:44:18,550
你想要跟我说什么吗?
Anything you want to say to me?

635
00:44:19,420 --> 00:44:23,290
我知道我不该相信她 我很清楚这一点
I know I shouldn't have trusted her. I know that for damn sure.

636
00:44:25,400 --> 00:44:28,200
我讨厌这一切
You know, I hate all this.

637
00:44:28,230 --> 00:44:30,870
一直都是
I always have.

638
00:44:30,900 --> 00:44:34,200
大概我只想要玩乐吧
I think all I ever wanted to do was play,

639
00:44:34,240 --> 00:44:37,440
尽情地欢笑和玩乐
just laugh and play.

640
00:44:40,080 --> 00:44:44,080
这里的人似乎都不会笑了
Yeah, it seems like nobody around here ever laughs anymore,

641
00:44:44,110 --> 00:44:46,750
除非是哪个麦考伊家的人受伤或者死了
except maybe when a McCoy gets maimed or killed.

642
00:44:51,220 --> 00:44:54,860
这对你来说是一个考验 爸爸
You know, that must be a trial for you, daddy,

643
00:44:54,890 --> 00:44:56,990
我不像你一样
me not being like you.

644
00:44:57,030 --> 00:44:59,130
你没有必要和我一样 约翰斯
You are who you are, Johnse.

645
00:44:59,160 --> 00:45:01,060
不 我是说
No, what I mean is,

646
00:45:01,100 --> 00:45:03,630
所有人都敬重你
everybody looks up to you,

647
00:45:03,670 --> 00:45:05,300
甚至连你的哥哥都是
I mean, even your older brothers.

648
00:45:06,740 --> 00:45:10,240
但是 却没有...
No, there ain't...

649
00:45:10,270 --> 00:45:12,370
没有人敬重我
there ain't nobody looking up to me.

650
00:45:14,710 --> 00:45:16,410
更可悲的是 有人说
Hell, there are those that say

651
00:45:16,450 --> 00:45:18,880
淡毛科顿都比我有用
Cotton Top's of more use.

652
00:45:20,480 --> 00:45:24,250
我都不知道该怎么待在这个家里
I don't know how to be in this family.

653
00:45:24,290 --> 00:45:26,020
我记得...
I mean, I got...

654
00:45:26,060 --> 00:45:27,520
记得所有的事情 你知道吗?
I got all the memories, you know?

655
00:45:27,560 --> 00:45:28,620
我记得所有发生过的事
I know all that's happened.

656
00:45:28,660 --> 00:45:29,860
只是...
I just...

657
00:45:33,660 --> 00:45:36,930
我并不后悔成为哈特菲尔德家族的一员
I don't have the hate that comes with being a Hatfield.

658
00:45:40,030 --> 00:45:41,600
当我抬头仰望的时候 爸爸
You know, I look up at that sky, pa,

659
00:45:41,640 --> 00:45:43,070
看到白云悠闲地飘过
and those clouds going by.

660
00:45:46,270 --> 00:45:47,740
我知道 它们正飞往
I'm telling you, I know they're headed

661
00:45:47,780 --> 00:45:52,510
一个和这里截然不同的地方
somewhere different than what we got here.

662
00:45:52,550 --> 00:45:55,680
我看过一些俄勒冈州的图片和故事
I seen these pictures and these stories about Oregon.

663
00:45:55,720 --> 00:45:58,550
天哪 他们有大片的树木可以砍伐
Man, they got these millions of trees to be logged,

664
00:45:58,590 --> 00:46:01,520
甚至比这里的更多
I mean, even more than here,

665
00:46:01,560 --> 00:46:06,530
河里的有肥美的鱼
wild rivers with fish long as your arm,

666
00:46:06,560 --> 00:46:08,660
不用跟麦考伊家的人打个你死我活
no McCoys to shoot at or get shot by.

667
00:46:11,000 --> 00:46:14,030
那里简直是人间天堂
That's heaven on earth.

668
00:46:14,070 --> 00:46:15,300
就是那样
That's what that is.

669
00:46:17,440 --> 00:46:18,840
那里就是我向往的地方
That's where I aim to go.

670
00:46:22,110 --> 00:46:25,110
在俄勒冈州你会停滞不前 约翰斯
You won't outrun yourself in Oregon, Johnse.

671
00:46:30,050 --> 00:46:32,190
我可以问你个问题吗?
Can I ask you a question?

672
00:46:36,190 --> 00:46:39,530
如果那天我掉下去了
If I would have fell in that day,

673
00:46:39,560 --> 00:46:41,660
吓跑了那些鱼...
scared those fish...

674
00:46:45,230 --> 00:46:47,030
你会任由我溺死吗?
Would you have let me drown?

675
00:48:00,440 --> 00:48:02,810
是一只老熊啊
That's a big old bear.

676
00:48:04,380 --> 00:48:07,950
它出现在我们背后 被约翰斯捕获了
Johnse bagged him when he come up behind us.

677
00:48:07,990 --> 00:48:09,290
我都没看到它
I never seen him.

678
00:48:09,320 --> 00:48:11,720
这孩子反应总是很快
That boy always did have quick reflexes.

679
00:48:14,930 --> 00:48:16,460
他只是...
He's just...

680
00:48:17,830 --> 00:48:21,060
拿那点俊俏的外表去玩了
Too damn handsome for his own good.

681
00:48:21,100 --> 00:48:22,270
虽然 除了英俊的外表
Though, he's a lot like his daddy,

682
00:48:22,300 --> 00:48:24,130
他很像他爸爸
except for the handsome part.

683
00:48:24,170 --> 00:48:27,940
这孩子一点儿也不像我
Boy's nothing like me.

684
00:48:27,970 --> 00:48:29,840
大冷天的早上你怎么来了?
What brings you out this frosty morn?

685
00:48:31,180 --> 00:48:36,150
我们的诉求有了回音
Well, I got news about our appeal.

686
00:48:36,280 --> 00:48:37,610
文迪州长正要把这些都
Governor Windy's taking it all the way

687
00:48:37,650 --> 00:48:40,050
上报给美国最高法院
to the United States supreme court.

688
00:48:40,080 --> 00:48:42,790
现在 我们也有法可依了 或许
Now we gonna be in the lawbooks, maybe.

689
00:48:42,820 --> 00:48:44,090
救孩子们出狱
Get our boys out of jail,

690
00:48:44,120 --> 00:48:45,560
回到家里去
back in their homes where they belong.

691
00:48:45,590 --> 00:48:47,820
任何一个懂点法律知识的人 
Anybody who knows anything about jurisprudence

692
00:48:47,860 --> 00:48:49,560
都说这是毫无疑问的
says there ain't no doubt.

693
00:48:50,590 --> 00:48:53,860
只有一个办法可以解决问题 哥哥
Only one thing gonna resolve this, big brother.

694
00:48:53,900 --> 00:48:56,270
而它绝不会是什么法律女士
And it ain't miss jurisprudence.

695
00:49:00,200 --> 00:49:01,740
不知道你们在这里计划什么 昂斯
I don't know what you're planning here, Anse,

696
00:49:01,770 --> 00:49:03,570
但这场该死的战争
but all this damn bloodshed

697
00:49:03,610 --> 00:49:04,840
是该结束了
and killing's got to stop.

698
00:49:06,240 --> 00:49:08,910
希望吉姆叔叔是最后一个牺牲者
Uncle Jim was the last straw.

699
00:49:11,310 --> 00:49:13,380
我要去自首
I'm turning myself in.

700
00:49:17,150 --> 00:49:19,860
你疯了?
You insane?

701
00:49:19,890 --> 00:49:22,820
那帮虚伪的家伙会让你脑袋开花的
Them blaggard's will shoot you down.

702
00:49:22,860 --> 00:49:24,890
我已经放话给佩里・克莱因了
I already sent word to Perry Cline.

703
00:49:24,930 --> 00:49:28,400
佩里・克莱因
Perry Cline.

704
00:49:28,430 --> 00:49:30,870
你认为那个卑鄙小人会信守承诺?
You think that skunk will keep his word?

705
00:49:30,900 --> 00:49:32,570
就这样定了 昂斯
It's done, Anse.

706
00:49:32,600 --> 00:49:34,300
我要用最恰当的方式来结束这场战争
I'm gonna fight this thing the best way I know how.

707
00:49:34,340 --> 00:49:36,310
在法庭上解决
I'm gonna fight it in the courtroom.

708
00:49:36,340 --> 00:49:37,810
在肯塔基的法庭上
In a Kentucky courtroom.

709
00:49:40,740 --> 00:49:42,640
但绝不是武力解决
But not with a damn gun.

710
00:49:44,810 --> 00:49:48,350
我的枪从没让我失望过 沃尔
Well, guns never failed me, wall,

711
00:49:48,380 --> 00:49:51,550
不像那些法官和律师
not like judges and lawyers.

712
00:49:56,390 --> 00:49:58,360
那就只能采取我们之间
Well, it's gonna be the way it's always been

713
00:49:58,390 --> 00:49:59,560
惯用的解决方式了 弟弟
between you and me, little brother.

714
00:49:59,600 --> 00:50:03,370
你用你的办法解决 我用我的方式处理
You gonna handle things your way, and I'm gonna do them my way.

715
00:50:03,400 --> 00:50:07,840
我从未告诉过你 我跟艾利生说过的一些话
Wall, I never told you about something I said to Ellison.

716
00:50:08,870 --> 00:50:11,540
或许是他所记得的最后一件事 或许不是
May be the last thing he remembered, maybe not,

717
00:50:11,570 --> 00:50:14,880
但却一直折磨着我
but it's haunted me ever since.

718
00:50:14,910 --> 00:50:17,310
所以现在 我不想...
So right now, I don't want to...

719
00:50:17,350 --> 00:50:18,950
现在 我不想对你说一些
Right now, I don't want to say something to you

720
00:50:18,980 --> 00:50:21,350
我将来会后悔的话
I'm gonna regret.

721
00:50:24,950 --> 00:50:28,290
你大可不必担心这些 昂斯
You ain't got no call to worry about that, Anse.

722
00:50:46,070 --> 00:50:47,910
嗨
Hey.

723
00:50:47,940 --> 00:50:52,910
我去会会法律女士 然后就来找你
I'll be seeing you right after I meet miss jurisprudence.

724
00:50:52,950 --> 00:50:56,020
驾! 
Ha! Come on.

725
00:51:05,630 --> 00:51:06,990
过来
Get over here.

726
00:51:17,640 --> 00:51:20,270
我是沃尔・哈特菲尔德法官
My name is justice wall Hatfield.

727
00:51:20,310 --> 00:51:23,140
依照应有的法律程序
I've surrendered myself on a Kentucky warrant

728
00:51:23,180 --> 00:51:24,980
我向肯塔基州法庭自首
for due process of the law.

729
00:51:28,310 --> 00:51:30,780
哈特菲尔德 你被逮捕了
Hatfield, you're under arrest.

730
00:51:30,820 --> 00:51:32,150
我是来自首的 菲利普斯
I'm turning myself in, Phillips.

731
00:51:32,190 --> 00:51:34,290
休想靠我得到任何赏金
You'll collect no bounty on me.

732
00:51:45,830 --> 00:51:48,530
分我一点儿吧 美女
Give me some of that, pretty lady.

733
00:52:01,310 --> 00:52:02,680
人家不要了
I ain't gonna do that.

734
00:52:02,720 --> 00:52:05,520
不 不要了
No, not now.

735
00:52:07,750 --> 00:52:10,420
嗨 嗨 介意把老大借我一会吗 女士?
Hey, hey, you mind if I borrow my boss from you, ma'am?

736
00:52:13,930 --> 00:52:15,460
《洛根旗帜》
Logan banner.

737
00:52:15,500 --> 00:52:17,530
说哈特菲尔德准备再次战争了
Says Hatfield's getting ready for war again,

738
00:52:16,500 --> 00:52:19,530
《洛根旗帜》
哈特菲尔德为战争做准备

739
00:52:17,560 --> 00:52:19,870
在三个州的各个五金店
buying every hardware store in three states

740
00:52:19,900 --> 00:52:21,770
大肆购买枪支弹药
out of guns and ammo.

741
00:52:21,800 --> 00:52:22,970
不过是个乡巴佬
Hillbilly dirt rag.

742
00:52:23,000 --> 00:52:24,070
不足为害
Means nothing.

743
00:52:25,100 --> 00:52:26,870
喝点吧
You need a drink.

744
00:52:29,370 --> 00:52:32,040
克莱因先生 什么事让你这么高兴?
Mr. Cline, what's your pleasure?

745
00:52:32,080 --> 00:52:33,810
已经痛饮了一番
Already got a fine libation.

746
00:52:37,050 --> 00:52:38,680
这不只是抓获沃尔・哈特菲尔德那么简单
I understand we're celebrating more

747
00:52:38,720 --> 00:52:41,490
值得我们好好庆祝一场
than the capture of wall Hatfield.

748
00:52:41,520 --> 00:52:44,250
见过弗兰克・菲利普斯夫人
Meet Miss Frank Phillips.

749
00:52:44,290 --> 00:52:45,820
恭喜
Congratulations.

750
00:52:45,860 --> 00:52:47,760
菲利普斯先生?
Mr. Phillips?

751
00:52:47,790 --> 00:52:49,460
菲利普斯先生?
Mr. Phillips?

752
00:52:49,490 --> 00:52:52,000
哈特菲尔德正在马特湾集合人马
A mob of Hatfields is forming over at mate creek,

753
00:52:52,030 --> 00:52:54,100
恶魔昂斯亲自带领
Devil Anse himself at the lead.

754
00:52:54,130 --> 00:52:56,970
好像朝这个方向过来了
Looks like they're a-fixing to ride this way.

755
00:52:57,000 --> 00:52:59,270
哈特菲尔德是想把他的亲戚们从监狱里救出去
Hatfield's busting his relatives out of jail.

756
00:52:59,300 --> 00:53:00,340
我们得阻止他 弗兰克
